claim.claim-text:
1. A method for using a dressing mechanism including the steps of:
providing a dressing mechanism, said dressing mechanism including a first section, a second section, and a third section; the first section being coupled to the second section and the second section being coupled to the third section; the first section and the third section comprising an elastic material; the first section and the third section each having a first side and a second side; a predetermined portion of the first side including an adhesive layer located thereon, the adhesive layer having a distal end and a proximal end;
applying said first section to a first predetermined location on an epidermis;
pulling said third section toward a second predetermined location on said epidermis;
applying said third section to said second predetermined location on said epidermis.

7. The method of claim 6 further including the steps of:
providing the first section with a first section margin;
providing the third section with a third section margin;
providing the second section with at least one channel, said at least one channel located between the first layer and the third layer of the second section and adapted to receive the first section margin and the third section margin, and wherein the second intermediate layer comprises an adhesive material;
providing the first section margin and the third section margin with at least one opening; and
engaging the first section margin and the third section margin in the channel, wherein the second intermediate layer adhesive material extends through the openings of the margins.
